\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104npm1665703214870.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/npm1665703214870.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/npm1665703214870.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"npm1665703214870\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the host identifiers or IP addresses to which the UHTTP component should connect directly,and not through a proxy server.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"npm1665703214870__topic_d138587e1_d138588e1_d138589e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"npm1665703214870__p_d138590e1_d138591e1_d138592e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$BYPASS</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">HostList</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"npm1665703214870__section_wxq_5ls_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604365e65\"> Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"npm1665703214870__p_d138596e1_d138597e1_d138598e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostList</var>—comma-separated list of host identifiers or IP addresses.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"npm1665703214870__section_tvy_5ls_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604365e77\"> Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"npm1665703214870__table_d16442e1_d16443e1_d16444e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> application files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzg1665702547028.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzg1665702547028.html\" title=\"Use the [PROXY_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to configure a proxy server for use by the UHTTP component.\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> none </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"npm1665703214870__section_sl2_vls_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604365e130\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"npm1665703214870__p_d138605e1_d138606e1_d138607e1\">On Microsoft Windows systems, if\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$BYPASS</span> is omitted, the UHTTP component uses the registry settings.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"npm1665703214870__pre_fzk_yms_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]\n$BYPASS = www.company.com, aweb.*\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"npm1665703214870__section_bmj_vls_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604365e145\"> Example: $BYPASS </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"npm1665703214870__pre_a3h_fns_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]\n$BYPASS = www.company.com, aweb.*\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wnk1665702545934.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UHTTP</a><p>The Uniface UHTTP component is an HTTP client that is used for sending and receiving HTTP requests and responses. It provides operations for executing HTTP requests used for web applications and RESTful web services.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530373\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530373\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$BYPASS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the host identifiers or IP addresses to which the UHTTP component should connect directly,and not through a proxy server. $BYPASS { = } HostList Arguments HostList —comma-separated list of host identifiers or IP addresses. Defaults Assignment file: application files Section: [PROXY_SETTINGS] Default value: none Description On Microsoft Windows systems, if $BYPASS is omitted, the UHTTP component uses the registry settings. [PROXY_SETTINGS] $BYPASS = www.company.com, aweb.* Copy Example: $BYPASS [PROXY_SETTINGS] $BYPASS = www.company.com, aweb.* Copy Related Links UHTTP The Uniface UHTTP component is an HTTP client that is used for sending and receiving HTTP requests and responses. It provides operations for executing HTTP requests used for web applications and RESTful web services. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}